Text: "I don't travel for days. I go live for months. I started from USA, where I\
  \ lived for 6 months across 10 states. I came to France and spent 6 months. I came\
  \ to Germany and travels for 6 months. I went to Switzerland and lived for 6 months.\
  \ Then I went to Austria and lived for 3 months in Bodensee area. Where we have\
  \ a triangle of Germany, Switzerland and Austria.\nThen i travels to Italy for two\
  \ weeks.\nNow I am I another part of Germany for next six months. All I know is\
  \ that Portugal and Spain is on my list. \nAnd I want to go live , meet people on\
  \ street, dance with them,tell them how I traveled and convince them you can also\
  \ do it if you have feelings to do it.\nRest will be storey."
